@startuml
title Sơ đồ tuần tự - Chức năng đăng nhập bằng Google

actor "Người dùng" as User
boundary "_LoginScreenState" as LoginScreenState
control "GoogleAuthService" as GoogleAuthService
control "GoogleSignIn" as GoogleSignIn
control "GoogleSignInAccount" as GoogleSignInAccount
control "AuthApiService" as AuthApiService
control "AuthController" as AuthController
control "AuthServiceImpl" as AuthServiceImpl
control "GoogleIdTokenVerifier" as GoogleIdTokenVerifier
database "ClientRepository" as ClientRepository
control "JwtUtil" as JwtUtil
control "UserMapper" as UserMapper
control "TokenStorageService" as TokenStorageService
database "SharedPreferences" as SharedPreferences
control "Navigator" as Navigator

User -> LoginScreenState: 1: bấm Đăng nhập bằng Google
activate LoginScreenState

LoginScreenState -> LoginScreenState: 2: _loginWithGoogle()
activate LoginScreenState

LoginScreenState -> GoogleAuthService: 3: gọi
activate GoogleAuthService
GoogleAuthService -> GoogleAuthService: 4: signIn()
activate GoogleAuthService

GoogleAuthService -> GoogleSignIn: 5: gọi
activate GoogleSignIn
GoogleSignIn -> GoogleSignIn: 6: signIn()
activate GoogleSignIn
deactivate GoogleSignIn
GoogleSignIn --> GoogleAuthService: 7: trả về kết quả
deactivate GoogleSignIn

deactivate GoogleAuthService
GoogleAuthService --> LoginScreenState: 8: trả về kết quả
deactivate GoogleAuthService

LoginScreenState -> GoogleAuthService: 9: gọi
activate GoogleAuthService
GoogleAuthService -> GoogleAuthService: 10: getIdToken()
activate GoogleAuthService

GoogleAuthService -> GoogleSignInAccount: 11: gọi
activate GoogleSignInAccount
GoogleSignInAccount -> GoogleSignInAccount: 12: authentication
activate GoogleSignInAccount
deactivate GoogleSignInAccount
GoogleSignInAccount --> GoogleAuthService: 13: trả về kết quả
deactivate GoogleSignInAccount

deactivate GoogleAuthService
GoogleAuthService --> LoginScreenState: 14: trả về kết quả
deactivate GoogleAuthService

LoginScreenState -> AuthApiService: 15: gọi
activate AuthApiService
AuthApiService -> AuthApiService: 16: loginWithGoogle(idToken)
activate AuthApiService

AuthApiService -> AuthController: 17: gọi API POST /auth/login/google
activate AuthController
AuthController -> AuthController: 18: loginWithGoogle(GoogleLoginRequest)
activate AuthController

AuthController -> AuthServiceImpl: 19: gọi
activate AuthServiceImpl
AuthServiceImpl -> AuthServiceImpl: 20: loginWithGoogle(GoogleLoginRequest)
activate AuthServiceImpl

AuthServiceImpl -> AuthServiceImpl: 21: verifyGoogleIdToken(idToken)
activate AuthServiceImpl

AuthServiceImpl -> GoogleIdTokenVerifier: 22: gọi
activate GoogleIdTokenVerifier
GoogleIdTokenVerifier -> GoogleIdTokenVerifier: 23: verify(idToken)
activate GoogleIdTokenVerifier
deactivate GoogleIdTokenVerifier
GoogleIdTokenVerifier --> AuthServiceImpl: 24: trả về kết quả
deactivate GoogleIdTokenVerifier

deactivate AuthServiceImpl

AuthServiceImpl -> ClientRepository: 25: gọi
activate ClientRepository
ClientRepository -> ClientRepository: 26: findByEmail(email)
activate ClientRepository
deactivate ClientRepository
ClientRepository --> AuthServiceImpl: 27: trả về kết quả
deactivate ClientRepository

AuthServiceImpl -> ClientRepository: 28: gọi
activate ClientRepository
ClientRepository -> ClientRepository: 29: save(Client)
activate ClientRepository
deactivate ClientRepository
ClientRepository --> AuthServiceImpl: 30: trả về kết quả
deactivate ClientRepository

AuthServiceImpl -> JwtUtil: 31: gọi
activate JwtUtil
JwtUtil -> JwtUtil: 32: generateToken(savedClient)
activate JwtUtil
deactivate JwtUtil
JwtUtil --> AuthServiceImpl: 33: trả về kết quả
deactivate JwtUtil

AuthServiceImpl -> UserMapper: 34: gọi
activate UserMapper
UserMapper -> UserMapper: 35: entityToResponse(savedClient)
activate UserMapper
deactivate UserMapper
UserMapper --> AuthServiceImpl: 36: trả về kết quả
deactivate UserMapper

deactivate AuthServiceImpl
AuthServiceImpl --> AuthController: 37: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthServiceImpl

deactivate AuthController
AuthController --> AuthApiService: 38: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthController

deactivate AuthApiService
AuthApiService --> LoginScreenState: 39: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthApiService

LoginScreenState -> TokenStorageService: 40: gọi
activate TokenStorageService
TokenStorageService -> TokenStorageService: 41: saveAuthSession(token, userInfo)
activate TokenStorageService

TokenStorageService -> SharedPreferences: 42: gọi
activate SharedPreferences
SharedPreferences -> SharedPreferences: 43: setString()/setInt()
activate SharedPreferences
deactivate SharedPreferences
SharedPreferences --> TokenStorageService: 44: trả về kết quả
deactivate SharedPreferences

deactivate TokenStorageService
TokenStorageService --> LoginScreenState: 45: trả về kết quả
deactivate TokenStorageService

LoginScreenState -> Navigator: 46: gọi
activate Navigator
Navigator -> Navigator: 47: pushNamedAndRemoveUntil()
activate Navigator
deactivate Navigator
Navigator --> LoginScreenState: 48: trả về kết quả
deactivate Navigator

deactivate LoginScreenState

LoginScreenState --> User: 49: điều hướng đến màn hình chính
deactivate LoginScreenState

@enduml
